// s87_fn_two_args_sub.vuma — sub(220, 65) = 220 - 65 = 155
// Expected exit code: 155
//
// Helper sub(x, y) = x - y. main calls sub(220, 65) -> 155.
// Two-arg function that subtracts. Distinct from s86_fn_two_
// args_sub (150), s82_fn_two_args_mul (56) and s78_fn_two_args_
